fields.name: Governance
fields.description: Disclose the organization’s governance around climate related risks and opportunities.

fields.name: Strategy
fields.description: Disclose the actual and potential impacts of climate-related risks and opportunities on the organization’s businesses, strategy, and financial planning where such information is material.

fields.name: Risk Management
fields.description: Disclose how the organization identifies, assesses, and manages climate-related risks.

fields.name: Metrics & Targets
fields.description: Disclose the metrics and targets used to assess and manage relevant climate-related risks and opportunities where such information is material.
